- Use a reliable QR code library like `qrcode.react` for React applications
- Ensure QR codes are generated with appropriate error correction levels
- Implement proper error handling for QR code generation
- Provide options for customizing QR code appearance (color, size, etc.)
- Ensure QR codes are accessible and can be easily scanned by mobile devices